{ Black covers his c6-Knight but also compromises his f8-Bishop in a line called the 'Cozio Defense', which is favored by few players today. }
4. O-O d6 5. d4 Bd7
{ Black reveals his point. He hasn't been forced to trade his strong e5-pawn. }
